<div class="home_bg" style="background-image: url('<%= image_path "demo_product.png" %>')">
</div>
<div class="home_container">
  <div style="margin-bottom: 5rem;">
    <div class="home_card_bg home_card_standalone">
    </div>
    <div class="home_card_content">
      <div class="home_card_left">
        <h1 class="home_title">Organisez vos vacances à plusieurs avec <strong>Tripster</strong></h1>
        <p>Finis les innombrables groupes de discussion pour organiser les vacances où rien n’avance comme il faut&nbsp!</p>
        <div class="home_card_links">
          <%= link_to "Créer un compte", new_user_registration_path, class:"btn btn-primary" %>
          <%= link_to "Se connecter", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-outline-primary" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="home_card_right">
        <%= image_tag "demo_product.png", class:"img-fluid" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="home_card_content home_card_left">
    <h2 class="home_title">Pourquoi <strong>Tripster</strong>&nbsp?</h2>
    <%= render partial: 'shared/data_blocs', locals: {user_count: @user_count, trip_count: @trip_count, review_count: @review_count} %>
    <p>Avec Tripster, choisissez votre <strong>destination</strong>, trouvez les <strong>dates</strong> qui conviennent à tous et dénichez ensemble la <strong>maison</strong> de vacances de vos rêves !</p>
  </div>
  <div class="home_footer mt-5">
    <h2 class="home_title mb-3">Installez l’application <strong>Tripster</strong> dès maintenant !</h2>
    <div class="home_card_links">
      <%= link_to "Installer Tripster", "#", class:"btn btn-primary" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>